                     <interp inst="t18210110-37-off214" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210110-37-off214" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18210110-37-cd215" type="crimeDate">16th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210110-37-off214 t18210110-37-cd215"></join>, 28 yards of calico, value 2 l. 6 s., the goods of 
                     
